            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>? Merc</supplied>urio August<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">Impera</supplied>toris Titi Caesari<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> templum a fundament<supplied reason="lost">is</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">mace</supplied>riem in circumitu et aedifici<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Textwiedergabe nach Galsterer - Galsterer. Doppelfeld mit weitergehenden Ergänzungen. Möglicherweise am Eingangstor der Umfassungsmauer des wieder aufgebauten Merkur-Tempels angebracht ( Galsterer - Galsterer 162).</p>
            </div>
